{"tid":1568853,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"［討論應對方法］915遊行前封站／遊行途中封站／警方自製劇本界入遊行及清場","createTime":"2019-09-14T11:58:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T13:49:56.000Z","uid":97523,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"4e73060024fb67490fc9abec2049ea8310d38fc5","tid":1568853,"uid":97523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T11:58:05.000Z","msg":"1. 遊行前已經封站 力阻遊行開始<br />\n2. 遊行途中封站 嘗試腰斬遊行 阻止遊行人士進入 <br />\n3. 以混亂為由/自製劇本令場面失控去進行清場行動 破壞遊行進行<br />\n<br />\n基本上以上三點都一定會發生<br />\n所以希望大家915一定要企出黎之餘<br />\n都要提前討論下行動細節<br />\n<br />\n不過可以肯定既係<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">人多就安全</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"84b86c8fc4a7c02f2c04240e40b78b10b47c3978","tid":1568853,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T11:58:28.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">[連儂文宣] 用CHINAZI喚醒藍絲廢老對共賊既不信任！</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1567514\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1567514</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YhY7uXD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYhY7uXD.jpg&h=5cadd691&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"464af018cc3480990beeba8ab045523ebb93e59d","tid":1568853,"uid":108337,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T11:59:57.000Z","msg":"其實有冇諗過18區報復奶共鋪頭"},{"pid":"a782e5d37ddea0608517df5f165d406da3106b7f","tid":1568853,"uid":97523,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T12:03:37.000Z","msg":"冇人理行動post"},{"pid":"65f61aad95e09eb3792228093a9995921fcc5ef7","tid":1568853,"uid":97523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T12:09:47.000Z","msg":"聽日係咪冇人出<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bd283705db09a0dd8871eef9c2cee5c28279f61","tid":1568853,"uid":143512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T12:14:53.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"e63a2bf996a9e686d2e2